experience.description:
Atar B2B was a Brazilian fintech that offered payments automation, Banking as a Service and Core Banking solutions. In 2021 it was acquired by Porto Seguro (PSSA3), one of the biggest companies in LatAm.

A little bit more about the company and its achievements: 

- We won 10 awards for innovation and entrepreneurship, in Brazil and abroad;

- Launched in 2016 the first wearable payment device in LatAm;

- We were named by the renowned business magazine 'Pequenas Empresas Grandes Negócios' as one of the 100 companies to keep an eye on;

- In 2019 we developed the official payment system of CONMEBOL Copa América 2019, one of the biggest sports event in the world, in partnership with Mastercard;

- We were one of the first companies in Brazil to offer APIs for payment / banking services. In the very beginning of what the market ended up defining as Banking as a Service.

- In 2021 we made an exit to Porto Seguro (PSSA3), one of the biggest companies in LatAm.
